      "widgets_values": [
        "Create a realistic full-body photo.\n\nUse the identity reference only for the person's identity: face, facial structure, hair, skin tone, age, and body proportions.\n\nUse the outfit/pose reference only for clothing design, colors, fabric texture, accessories, silhouette, and body pose.\n\nThe final image must show the person from the identity reference wearing the outfit from the outfit/pose reference and adopting the pose from the outfit/pose reference.\n\nDo not copy the face, hair, identity, or body shape from the outfit/pose reference. Keep the face recognizable as the identity reference. Preserve the outfit colors, patterns, collar, sleeves, hem, shoes, and accessories. Natural lighting, coherent anatomy, realistic hands, clean background."
