    {
      "id": 25,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        -650,
        1180
      ],
      "size": [
        980,
        300
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 6,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "=== DGX Spark outfit-first / identity-late stock v3 ===\nPurpose: reduce identity-reference clothing leakage using only stock ComfyUI nodes.\n\nCreated on 2026-06-07 after stock v2 showed no visible improvement:\n- First successful run preserved the identity face but pulled identity-reference clothing too strongly.\n- stock v2 changed reference input scale but did not improve, so simultaneous reference mixing is the likely problem.\n- This version separates references by sampler pass instead of only scaling them.\n- Pass 1 uses only the outfit/pose reference to establish clothing, pose, framing, and background.\n- Pass 2 uses only the identity reference on the low-sigma late steps to recover face/identity with less chance of replacing clothing.\n- SplitSigmas is set to 7, so identity is applied only in the last 3 of 10 steps.\n- Identity reference input scale: 1.00 MP.\n- Outfit/pose reference input scale: 2.80 MP.\n- Keeps Turbo r128 at 0.45.\n- Keeps SNOFS omitted.\n- Keeps DWPose/OpenPose, VTON, Qwen-Image-Edit, ReferenceLatentPlus, and Flux2KleinEnhancer omitted.\n\nIf pose remains weak but clothing improves, next step is DWPose/OpenPose. If face weakens too much, lower SplitSigmas back to 6 or raise identity reference scale slightly."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
